Closing Principle
The instrument supports the work. The human provides the context, judgment, compassion, and accountability.
HCOS™ Healthcare Instruments are intended to help people see more clearly without surrendering the responsibility to think, understand, protect, and care.
Think Well.
Teach Well.
Understand Well.
Grow Well.
Lead with Love.
See the Whole System.
Protect with Wisdom, Compassion, and Presence.
Help People Flourish.

